data.description: HUGE  Price Reduction! Motivated Seller. Bring all offers and come see this very well kept and move in ready 3 BR 3 full BA home in convenient 55+ community with beautiful mountain views. Lawn Care, including mowing, edging, sprinkler maintenance, aeration, fertilizing, and pest treatment keeping the outside of your new home looking great! Don't worry about snow removal, that is taken care of including streets, driveway, sidewalks and steps. A tiled entryway opens to vaulted ceilings in the living and family rooms, the kitchen has a large island with granite countertops, soft close cabinets, and subway tile back splash.  Just off the kitchen and breakfast nook is a covered patio with composite deck and vinyl railings. Deep 2 car garage with sensor illumination and insulated doors. There's new carpet in the living room and in the finished basement with large storage area where the shelving stays! A 10-year smoke alarm system and attractive fireplace that works with the flip of a switch. A new furnace motor in December 2023. High efficiency Maytag Washer and Dryer recently serviced and in excellent condition and a refrigerator with lighted freezer and ice maker included! Close to shopping, walking trails, parks, freeway access and many outdoor activities.
